Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.62,0:00:07.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,By day she is a happy student\Nat St. Paulia School.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:11.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But at night, she becomes\Nthe phantom thief Saint Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.65,0:00:13.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,to do good deeds for all who come\Nasking for help from Seira...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:15.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,a nun in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.70,0:00:20.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Looking to capture the elusive Saint Tail\Nis an amateur detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.88,0:00:22.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,and Meimi's classmate, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:25.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,As for Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.13,0:00:28.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,she may have more than a bit of\Ninterest in such a determined boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi's lover is a hedgehog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:43.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That mom of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:46.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's Sunday, and she has to make me\Ngo do the grocery shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:04.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:21.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What is it?! What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:25.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're a really rude creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.77,0:01:26.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:41.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:58.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If it's the cat, it went that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:01:59.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:02.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please watch the shop\Nfor a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What? Hang on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:06.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:09.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:24.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What could this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:29.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Y... You!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're the rude one\NI met the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:34.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Humph!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:46.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.39,0:02:50.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're all alone, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:56.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, cute little hedgehog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:06.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're the only person that this\Nhedgehog has warmed up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:08.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My name is Meimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:15.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll come to see you ever day from\Nnow on! So let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:22.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:24.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:25.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it!\NCome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.86,0:03:27.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.64,0:03:33.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, want to stop for\Nice cream on the way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:37.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's a new shop that just opened\Nbeside the park on 2nd Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I've got something to do today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:41.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Something to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:43.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A date.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:44.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:46.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yup! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:52.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Have you had a nice day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hi! Back again?\NYou're fond of her, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:11.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask your mother and\Nfather if you can buy her as a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:14.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I promise I won't sell her to anyone\Nelse until you get their permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:15.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:18.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You won't sell her\Nto anyone else until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sure. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:25.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, my little hedgehog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mister, I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.17,0:04:29.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:35.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:39.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This hedgehog, sell him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But it's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Look, I said I want this hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please Dad, can I?\NCan I have the hedgehog?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:58.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Did you say hedgehog?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:01.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NI even have a name for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.29,0:05:03.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll call her Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:08.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The ring that dad bought you\Nis a ruby, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my engagement ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's why I named her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... a ruby...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:26.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It does bring back memories\Nof the old days, doesn't it, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.28,0:05:29.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Eimi, you haven't changed\Na bit since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:35.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why, dear, you haven't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Eimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:39.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Genichiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hello, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:45.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, gee, Meimi, were you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Of course, where else would I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:51.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Then it's all right for me to have\Na hedgehog named Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:53.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.61,0:05:57.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It helps, having easy-going parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:02.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:04.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:06.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:09.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You promised you wouldn't sell her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:13.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He insisted on buying it.\NHe wouldn't take no for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:16.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Moping will get me nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:34.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Ruby is having\Na nice life, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Right! I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:43.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Polar Tear?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:46.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a beautiful diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:50.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Legend says it's a teardrop\Nof the North Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:55.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I shared the diamond with Hayase,\Nan old friend from my school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:07:01.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We took turns, keeping the gem\Nfor two months at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:05.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That was our agreement.\NI never expected he would betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He betrayed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:08.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:13.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday was the day I was to receive\Nthe diamond for the next two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:19.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hayase, what are you saying?\NYou haven't given the diamond to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:24.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous, Kamimura.\NOf course I gave you the diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you doubt me, search the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.05,0:07:34.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Kamimura... maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:40.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're not trying to keep the\Ndiamond all to yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:42.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:44.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's what you're trying to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:46.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:49.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof that\NI didn't give you the diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:05.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's the story I heard today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:09.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They finally called the police\Nand searched the house, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:11.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They couldn't find the diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:16.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And according to the contract,\Nif the Polar Tear is lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:20.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,the one that loses the gem\Nhas to pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:22.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,On top of stealing the diamond...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:31.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hayase is holding him\Nliable for the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:38.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm really angry! Phantom Saint Tail\Nshall retrieve that diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:44.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?\NYou're not usually this touchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:48.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:50.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I went to the pet shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:52.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The pet shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.56,0:08:55.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Someone bought my hedgehog!\NShe's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:59.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'd even thought up some hedgehog\Nmagic to use on the next caper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let us continue\Nfrom line 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:35.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Asuka! Read!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:50.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:56.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Tonight, I'll be at the Hayase\Nmansion to get the Polar Tear"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.02,0:09:58.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Signed, Saint Tail."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:14.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:17.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.78,0:10:26.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, forgive me, for I use\Nno gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:32.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:59.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:02.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:04.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:07.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,To help me forget\Nmy little hedgehog...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna nail this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I don't need your security!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:18.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The police checked it out, but\Nthe Polar Tear is not in this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:20.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Whatever Saint Tail\Nis supposed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:22.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,how can she steal something\Nthat isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:28.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But Saint Tail sent me a warning\Nthat she'll show up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:33.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:36.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The Mayor's special\Nbadge of investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:39.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm staking out\Nyour home, Mr. Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:51.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The question is where's the diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:54.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That must be Hayase.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:05.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But why is my\Nhedgehog Ruby here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I must say, this is ingenious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:14.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No one would ever think that the\NPolar Tear is inside your stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.51,0:12:18.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible thing to do!\NAbsolutely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:22.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:24.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:27.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's rude of me,\Nbut are you really sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:29.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,the Polar Tear is\Nnot in the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Persistent, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:35.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I handed the diamond\Nover to Kamimura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:38.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A hedgehog?\NWhat an unusual pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:42.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:50.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:51.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:01.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's Saint Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:09.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn, you're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:12.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,My Polar Tear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:16.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hang on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:17.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They sure are persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:36.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What the... why are you on my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:44.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:48.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you chasing me for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:52.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Stop running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.72,0:13:57.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.! I'm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:05.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You brat!\NWhy are you running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:07.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm not running away,\NI'm chasing Saint Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Saint Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.70,0:14:18.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:22.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hand over that hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:26.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You just wait right there!\NI'll get you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:30.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:33.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How hopeless can he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:50.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:13.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You little pest! Hand it over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold that elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's no use trying\Nto escape like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:31.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up to you\Nin the other elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:34.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:34.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:38.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:42.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! The hedgehog is all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:55.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Look this way, Saint Tail.\NMaybe I can see her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:57.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I just want to get\Na look at her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:15:58.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Show your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:00.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:00.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:09.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll be getting off here. Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:13.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:15.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Do something, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Stop being a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:21.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Too bad that elevator doesn't stop\Nuntil it gets to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:31.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait right there!\NI'll get you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:35.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I know I should probably\Njust escape now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:37.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:44.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It really bugs me.\NWhy can't I just let that guy be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait, it's coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:56.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What a stupid phantom,\Nshe's going to follow us up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:00.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:04.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail, we've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hand over my hedgehog!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.87,0:17:13.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:19.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I'd get a chance\Nto use my hedgehog magic so soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One! Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:25.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:43.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were able to cough it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.98,0:17:45.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:50.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for being bad\Nand hoarding the gem all to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:57.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:04.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.76,0:18:06.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the rest for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:11.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,A star?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:23.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the Polar Tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:24.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:27.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why did she give this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.14,0:18:28.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, son!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:30.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.51,0:18:33.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hayase is out cold down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.66,0:18:36.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But I'm arresting him\Non charges offraud.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:40.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And this is Mr. Kamimura,\Nthe owner of the diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:42.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,the Polar Tear is safe,\Nthank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.07,0:18:47.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ah... don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:51.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Saint Tail, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:59.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well now, Hayase has been caught.\NWanna come live at my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:05.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Okay! One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is to celebrate our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Let's be good friends!
